name: Delta (Toronto Raptors) 757-232 [N664DN] Dusk Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
An NBA charter! We don't get these too often! Here we have N664DN, a 26-year old 757-200 carrying the Toronto Raptors after their game in Vancouver. They'll be playing the Denver Nuggets on Monday October 3rd, and that team was flown in earlier on the other Delta 757 in this video (N663DN). This video includes the arrival, some players getting off the aircraft, and the buses driving away. Enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
